## Quick Commands
```bash
# Docker Development (RECOMMENDED) üê≥
scripts\wadm-dev.bat start              # Start complete stack (30s)
scripts\wadm-dev.bat status             # Check all services
scripts\wadm-dev.bat logs               # View API logs
python scripts/test-docker.py           # Test all services

# Legacy Local Development
python main.py                          # Run collectors
python api_server.py                    # Start API
python test_api.py                      # Test endpoints

